<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 08:09:02 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>根据战时规定，以色列在没有举行听证会的情况下将巴勒斯坦被拘留者关押了八天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/using-wartime-provision-israel-holds-palestinian-detainees-for-eight-days-with-no-hearing/0000018d-8558-df76-a1fd-cff987c60000</link><description>以色列国防军和警方依赖军法中很少使用的反恐条款，导致拘留期更长。在一个案件中，七人被关押了八天，直到法官裁定他们是犯罪受害者</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 04:00:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/using-wartime-provision-israel-holds-palestinian-detainees-for-eight-days-with-no-hearing/0000018d-8558-df76-a1fd-cff987c60000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦人向约旦河西岸军队哨所开枪，被以色列国防军击毙；来自黎巴嫩的火箭降落在以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-live/blinken-hamas-response-creates-space-for-agreement-netanyahu-slams-delusional-demands/0000018d-868c-d0de-af8d-8ebc4d630000</link><description>勇敢对布林肯：哈马斯的回应是为了确保以色列的拒绝，他们的立场将延长战争 ■ 联合国秘书长对以色列国防军预计向拉法推进感到“震惊”，布林肯就此事向内塔尼亚胡和勇敢发出警告 ■ 哈马斯寻求俘虏、交换人质并撤出以色列部队参与135天停火提议</description><pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 02:36:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article-live/blinken-hamas-response-creates-space-for-agreement-netanyahu-slams-delusional-demands/0000018d-868c-d0de-af8d-8ebc4d630000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的妻子出庭听取以色列前总检察长在总理腐败案审判中作证</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wife-in-court-to-hear-israels-former-ag-testify-in-pms-graft-trial/0000018d-8558-df76-a1fd-cff9c6130000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡因接受好莱坞大亨和澳大利亚商人价值数十万谢克尔的礼物而受审，其中最著名的是雪茄和香槟，他否认了这些指控</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 22:31:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-08/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wife-in-court-to-hear-israels-former-ag-testify-in-pms-graft-trial/0000018d-8558-df76-a1fd-cff9c6130000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军称，以色列军队在袭击西岸难民营时打死三名武装巴勒斯坦人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/israeli-forces-kill-three-armed-palestinians-in-raid-on-west-bank-refugee-camp-idf-says/0000018d-852f-d0de-af8d-8d3f35ac0000</link><description>以色列国防军表示，其中一名目标人员被描述为难民营的“高级特工”，涉嫌向以色列军队开枪并参与恐怖活动</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 21:02:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/israeli-forces-kill-three-armed-palestinians-in-raid-on-west-bank-refugee-camp-idf-says/0000018d-852f-d0de-af8d-8d3f35ac0000</guid></item><item><title>被释放的人质含泪敦促内塔尼亚胡确保释放被哈马斯扣押的剩余以色列人</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/netanyahu-slams-hamas-demands-as-freed-israeli-hostages-plea-him-to-avoid-moral-stain/0000018d-8501-df76-a1fd-cff1a7980000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在新闻发布会上表示，“后天就是哈马斯的后天”，并坚称“全面胜利”是他唯一可以接受的结果。一名72岁的获释人质向总理呼吁：“如果你继续‘瓦解哈马斯’的路线，就不会有任何人质可以拯救了”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 20:57:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/netanyahu-slams-hamas-demands-as-freed-israeli-hostages-plea-him-to-avoid-moral-stain/0000018d-8501-df76-a1fd-cff1a7980000</guid></item><item><title>马克龙向 10 月 7 日遇难者家属提供了内塔尼亚胡不会提供的东西</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-07/ty-article/.highlight/macron-gave-october-7-victims-families-what-netanyahu-wont/0000018d-84e7-d424-abad-9fffc9d30000</link><description>在以色列，仍被哈马斯扣押的 100 多名人质的家人被迫乞求与内阁成员会面，并了解停火协议的最新进展，以便让他们回家</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 20:29:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-02-07/ty-article/.highlight/macron-gave-october-7-victims-families-what-netanyahu-wont/0000018d-84e7-d424-abad-9fffc9d30000</guid></item><item><title>本-格维尔加强对执法部门的控制，以色列媒体顾问接受警方讯问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-media-adviser-questioned-by-police-as-ben-gvirs-grip-on-law-enforcement-deepens/0000018d-84c1-d424-abad-9fd9cee40000</link><description>伊齐克·埃尔罗夫（Itzik Elrov）发布了一张照片，其中以色列交通部长穿着一件用沾满鲜血的爆米花制成的连衣裙。一名高级观察员表示，警方对他的讯问反映出本-格维尔的“帮派风气”对以色列警察的影响日益加深</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 19:35:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-media-adviser-questioned-by-police-as-ben-gvirs-grip-on-law-enforcement-deepens/0000018d-84c1-d424-abad-9fd9cee40000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 124 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-124/0000018d-84d9-df76-a1fd-cff94e420000</link><description>哈马斯提出 135 天停火计划 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡称哈马斯提议“妄想” ■ 由卡塔尔/埃及斡旋的新一轮人质释放协议谈判定于周四开始 ■ 沙特阿拉伯表示，如果没有独立的巴勒斯坦国，就不可能与以色列实现正常化■ 战争开始 124 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 18:41:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.highlight/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-124/0000018d-84d9-df76-a1fd-cff94e420000</guid></item><item><title>以色列外交部夸耀巴勒斯坦 LGBTQ 庇护裁决；内政部长寻求逆转</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/foreign-ministry-boasts-lgbtq-palestinian-asylum-ruling-interior-minister-seeks-reversal/0000018d-83fb-dfd5-adff-dbfbc7a00000</link><description>特拉维夫的一名法官最近裁定，因性取向受到威胁的巴勒斯坦人可以在以色列申请庇护。外交部发布了一条推文庆祝这一裁决，然后将其删除</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 16:31:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/foreign-ministry-boasts-lgbtq-palestinian-asylum-ruling-interior-minister-seeks-reversal/0000018d-83fb-dfd5-adff-dbfbc7a00000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦国能在经济上实现生存吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/could-a-palestinian-state-ever-be-economically-viable/0000018d-8357-dfd5-adff-dbf7ce830000</link><description>约旦河西岸和加沙拥有一些资产可以用来建设繁荣的经济，但负债也更大。拜登的计划未能解决这个问题</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 15:49:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/could-a-palestinian-state-ever-be-economically-viable/0000018d-8357-dfd5-adff-dbf7ce830000</guid></item><item><title>法国为哈马斯 10 月 7 日袭击事件受害者举行全球首个悼念仪式</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/france-holds-worlds-first-memorial-ceremony-for-victims-of-oct-7-attack/0000018d-840e-df76-a1fd-cfffd4b10000</link><description>42 名法裔以色列遇难者的约 100 名亲属参加了在巴黎举行的活动，总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙 (Emmanuel Macron) 宣布“今天有 6800 万法国公民哀悼”。一位悲伤的母亲告诉媒体，“在以色列，我们感觉自己被忽视了，感谢法国，我的女儿不会被忘记”</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 15:45:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/france-holds-worlds-first-memorial-ceremony-for-victims-of-oct-7-attack/0000018d-840e-df76-a1fd-cfffd4b10000</guid></item><item><title>“未经证实的指控”：英国第四频道猛烈抨击以色列对近东救济工程处的指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/unproven-allegations-u-k-channel-4-slams-israels-charge-against-unrwa/0000018d-837c-d636-adef-cffe76790000</link><description>对联合国巴勒斯坦难民救济机构的指控是在一份以色列情报简报中提出的，最初是在《华尔街日报》上报道的。英国第四频道声称“没有证据”证明以色列对近东救济工程处工作人员的指控</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 15:28:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/unproven-allegations-u-k-channel-4-slams-israels-charge-against-unrwa/0000018d-837c-d636-adef-cffe76790000</guid></item><item><title>停火协议将是哈马斯的巨大胜利，但以色列别无选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-cease-fire-deal-would-be-a-huge-victory-for-hamas-but-israel-has-no-choice/0000018d-8346-d361-a9cd-e7ee36500000</link><description>2011 年，我参与谈判的哈马斯与以色列人质协议规定，以 1,000 多名巴勒斯坦囚犯换取一名以色列士兵。这本应该是以色列最后一次不得不赎回其公民，但今天，哈马斯占了上风</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:59:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-02-07/ty-article-opinion/.premium/a-cease-fire-deal-would-be-a-huge-victory-for-hamas-but-israel-has-no-choice/0000018d-8346-d361-a9cd-e7ee36500000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人质及其家人为内塔尼亚胡和加兰特的吹嘘付出代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-pay-the-price-for-netanyahu-and-gallants-boasting/0000018d-8363-d361-a9cd-e7eb4bec0000</link><description>即使总理和国防部长的目的是削弱哈马斯在谈判中的地位，他们对哈马斯领导人被暗杀的无休止的谈论似乎已经取代了行动</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:56:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-hostages-families-pay-the-price-for-netanyahu-and-gallants-boasting/0000018d-8363-d361-a9cd-e7eb4bec0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军预备役军人在加沙战斗中受伤几周后死于真菌感染</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-reservist-dies-of-fungal-infection-weeks-after-suffering-wounds-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-83aa-dfd5-adff-dbbbc75a0000</link><description>在各种治疗未能治愈感染后，这名26岁的男子服用了卫生部批准的特殊用途的实验药物</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:50:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-reservist-dies-of-fungal-infection-weeks-after-suffering-wounds-in-gaza-fighting/0000018d-83aa-dfd5-adff-dbbbc75a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列选择欧洲电视网参赛者，呼吁禁止参加加沙战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-selects-eurovision-contestant-amid-calls-to-ban-participation-over-gaza-war/0000018d-832d-dfd5-adff-dbbda1b90000</link><description>20 岁的伊登·戈兰 (Eden Golan) 在赢得以色列歌唱电视节目 HaKokhav Haba 后获得提名，她将面临围绕以色列参加国际歌唱比赛已经存在的争议</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:45:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/israel-selects-eurovision-contestant-amid-calls-to-ban-participation-over-gaza-war/0000018d-832d-dfd5-adff-dbbda1b90000</guid></item><item><title>“胜利在于框架”：六日战争期间大胆的以色列音乐剧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/movies/2024-02-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/victory-is-a-matter-of-framing-the-daring-israeli-musical-set-during-the-six-day-war/0000018d-5954-d0fc-a9bd-5f5d002a0000</link><description>一位患有创伤后应激障碍 (PTSD) 的以色列退伍军人偶然发表的评论，让编剧兼导演埃里兰·佩莱德开始了长达七年的冒险之旅。最终的成果是他 1967 年创作的《胜利》，这是一部色彩缤纷但极其复杂的音乐剧，与当今的以色列息息相关</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 14:30:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/culture/movies/2024-02-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/victory-is-a-matter-of-framing-the-daring-israeli-musical-set-during-the-six-day-war/0000018d-5954-d0fc-a9bd-5f5d002a0000</guid></item><item><title>解释者：美国制裁的以色列定居者是谁？他们的目标意味着什么？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/who-are-the-israeli-settlers-sanctioned-by-the-u-s-and-what-does-their-targeting-mean/0000018d-8233-d636-adef-ceffc2980000</link><description>以色列银行开始封锁犹太定居者的账户，以遵守拜登政府因袭击巴勒斯坦人而对四名以色列定居者实施的制裁。他们是谁？对未来可能产生哪些影响？</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 13:49:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/who-are-the-israeli-settlers-sanctioned-by-the-u-s-and-what-does-their-targeting-mean/0000018d-8233-d636-adef-ceffc2980000</guid></item><item><title>人质仍然是辛瓦尔最有效的杠杆，也是他在谈判中唯一讨价还价的筹码</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/hostages-remain-sinwars-most-effective-lever-and-his-only-bargaining-chip-in-talks/0000018d-82b0-d6dc-ab9f-cffdfb5b0000</link><description>哈马斯在加沙和国外的领导层非常清楚，只有人质问题才能让数以万计的以色列人走上街头，也只有这场斗争才能迫使内塔尼亚胡处理棘手的问题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 13:07:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article/.premium/hostages-remain-sinwars-most-effective-lever-and-his-only-bargaining-chip-in-talks/0000018d-82b0-d6dc-ab9f-cffdfb5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列心理学家阻止下一个摩萨德叛徒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-psychologists-stopping-the-next-mossad-traitor/0000018d-7f37-daa1-a9fd-7f3ff0e80000</link><description>以色列情报部门不仅使用心理分析来分析敌人，还用于筛查和治疗在敌对领土上进行作战活动的人员，因为他们知道他们冒着生命危险</description><pubDate>Wed, 07 Feb 2024 12:58:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-02-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-psychologists-stopping-the-next-mossad-traitor/0000018d-7f37-daa1-a9fd-7f3ff0e80000</guid></item></channel></rss>